{"tid":475860,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)宇宙騎士BLADE","createTime":"2017-11-21T13:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T16:21:20.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a16f9e171a7ee00eec4bef07f76131db8ca1658","tid":475860,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=2Fy9sHg1tkMoLIOMRMTSnr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b8d8cee6\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=2Fy9sHg1tkMoLIOMRMTSnr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2ee7837f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=2Fy9sHg1tkMoLIOMRMTSnr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=43dc98e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170727/819971fabcd642a6a42fb9708477131b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20170727%2F819971fabcd642a6a42fb9708477131b.jpeg&h=9661b6c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合地球歷192年，神秘宇宙生命體侵略地球。外宇宙開發基地意外的搭救了一個從天而降的奇怪人類，而他居然可以變身為身著堅硬盔甲的戰士和怪獸進行抗衡。瀕臨滅亡的人類還是 抓住了這根救命稻草，天外來客以D-boy（Dangerous boy）的身體在外宇宙開發基地留了下來，經歷多次拯救地球的戰鬥後，人類把他稱為宇宙騎士<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=2Fy9sHg1tkMoLIOMRMTSnr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5d0983ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=2Fy9sHg1tkMoLIOMRMTSnr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=eb30f957\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811a9dc7e3ce669058ba0a448c9745fbb6034bee","tid":475860,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8d4ff130f12d16701f12f124cfd2b05fcf4042","tid":475860,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9323398b0127866d57962ffd0a2f218665f38fc1","tid":475860,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd10523fe18c35ca2741ba087a38b5582a121b23","tid":475860,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T18:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img 